The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 was introduced in 2000.
The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 featured a dual Garmin 430 panel.
The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 featured a KFC-225 autopilot.
The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 featured a leather interior.
The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 featured a two-bladed McCauley propeller.
The dual Garmin 430 panel in the Mooney M20R Ovation 2 was replaced with a Garmin 530/430 panel in 2001.
A limited Platinum Edition of the Mooney M20R Ovation 2 was offered with advanced avionics.
The Platinum Edition of the Mooney M20R Ovation 2 included airframe upgrades.
The Platinum Edition of the Mooney M20R Ovation 2 included cabin upgrades.

The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 DX was introduced in 2005.
The Mooney M20R Ovation 2 GX was introduced in 2005.
One Mooney M20R Ovation 2 DX was built in 2005.

text:
Certified June 30, 1994.  199 total built; 21 (1994), 54 (1995), 20 (1996), 36 (1997), 41 (1998), and 27 (1999).
M20R Ovation 2, introduced in 2000.  As Ovation but with a dual Garmin 430 panel, a KFC-225 autopilot, a leather interior, and a two-bladed McCauley propeller.  The dual Garmin 430 panel was replaced with a similar Garmin 530/430 panel in 2001.  A limited Platinum Edition was offered with advanced avionics and airframe and cabin upgrades.  131 total built; 55 (2000), 12 (2001), 8 (2002), 28 (2003), and 28 (2004).
M20R Ovation 2 DX, introduced in 2005 alongside the Ovation 2 GX.  One built in 2005.
